scopecontent.p:
General topics of discussion in Dr. Kehr's correspondence
         include: exchanges of seed, pollen, cuttings and plants;
         registration of new hybrids, research on rhododendrons;
         publications; gardens; botanical expeditions; plant crosses;
         rhododendron subjects for talks at meetings; rhododendron
         controversies and disagreements; plant shipments; plant
         diseases; azaleas and other flowering plants; tissue culture;
         the merits of various rhododendrons, and magnolias.
